  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK360">
<l>kāmam vekuḷi mayakka mivaimūṉṟi</l>
<l>ṉāmaṅ keṭakkeṭu nōy</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If the very names of these three things, desire, anger, and confusion of mind, be destroyed, then will also perish evils (which flow from them).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
